Dialogue: 0,0:00:01.77,0:00:05.43,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Raise your eyes you can see\Nshooting stars up in the night sky
Dialogue: 0,0:00:09.56,0:00:13.04,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Raise your eyes you can see\Nshooting stars up in the night sky
Dialogue: 0,0:00:32.49,0:00:33.46,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,One, two...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:33.46,0:00:36.38,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,The sound resonates\NInto my heart, so hard and deep
Dialogue: 0,0:00:36.38,0:00:40.32,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,A field of stars spans endlessly\NAnd through it I carve a passageway
Dialogue: 0,0:00:40.32,0:00:42.19,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,In step with time as generations change
Dialogue: 0,0:00:42.19,0:00:44.19,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Close your eyes and listen closely
Dialogue: 0,0:00:44.19,0:00:47.58,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Shooting stars stream on silently…\Nuntil the goodbye
Dialogue: 0,0:00:48.19,0:00:50.32,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Keep the light inside of you,\Nnever give up don't ever lose
Dialogue: 0,0:00:50.32,0:00:52.09,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Transcend time and you will prove,\Nthere is a special place for you
Dialogue: 0,0:00:52.09,0:00:53.93,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,A blaze of glory is there,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:53.93,0:00:56.09,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,It's all a part of our estate;\Nlife is our story to create
Dialogue: 0,0:00:57.97,0:01:01.64,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Raise your eyes you can see\Nshooting stars up in the night sky
Dialogue: 0,0:01:01.64,0:01:05.54,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Wishes speak from ages old by voice of light\NThroughout the age, never fade away
Dialogue: 0,0:01:05.54,0:01:09.29,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,A secret fire, a scream of light,\Nvoices calling through twilight
Dialogue: 0,0:01:09.29,0:01:11.22,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Cast your thoughts to the wind,\Nhang your wishes on the moon
Dialogue: 0,0:01:11.22,0:01:13.44,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Live your life with all your strength\Nfor dreams will reach you very soon
Dialogue: 0,0:01:13.44,0:01:16.75,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Raise your eyes you can see\Nshooting stars up in the night sky
Dialogue: 0,0:01:17.10,0:01:19.07,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Wishes speak from ages old\Nby voice of light
Dialogue: 0,0:01:19.07,0:01:21.16,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Throughout the age,\Nnever fade away
Dialogue: 0,0:01:21.16,0:01:24.76,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Someday your dream will find\Nits place somewhere
Dialogue: 0,0:01:25.05,0:01:28.67,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Keep shining like a star
Dialogue: 0,0:01:28.67,0:01:34.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:34.84,0:01:35.51,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Yuzu...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:39.09,0:01:41.05,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,You're so noisy...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:41.29,0:01:43.80,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,One hostage is good enough...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:57.29,0:01:58.10,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Karin!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:59.84,0:02:00.89,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Good.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:00.89,0:02:02.97,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,I still have my hostage.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:02.97,0:02:05.14,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,I've been waiting for you,\NSoul Reaper.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:06.29,0:02:07.01,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Karin!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:08.63,0:02:09.63,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Ichigo...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:13.88,0:02:15.35,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Furukawa Family Plot
Dialogue: 0,0:02:17.42,0:02:18.35,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,That bastard...!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:29.29,0:02:30.42,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,What's going on?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:34.29,0:02:35.32,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Why you--!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:35.32,0:02:37.29,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,You're the one who was\Nat the riverbank, aren't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:38.13,0:02:39.13,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Six years ago!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:39.29,0:02:40.59,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,So what are you doing here?!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:41.55,0:02:42.38,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Six years ago?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.13,0:02:44.29,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Ichigo, don't tell me...!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:44.46,0:02:47.96,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah... I tried to help her back then.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.29,0:02:50.92,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,But when I realized it, she was gone...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.00,0:02:53.05,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,and my mom was...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.71,0:02:55.67,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,My mom was...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.59,0:02:58.34,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Six years ago, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.00,0:03:01.71,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,I don't remember things so long ago.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.59,0:03:03.70,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,I see...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.70,0:03:05.36,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,This is very interesting.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.63,0:03:20.24,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Grand Fisher!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.55,0:03:21.42,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,That's his code name.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.29,0:03:24.29,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,He hides himself and\Ngives the lure
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.29,0:03:27.21,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,that grows out of his head\Na human appearance.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.88,0:03:29.30,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,And when he finds those\Nwho are able to see it...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.22,0:03:33.06,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,In other words, those who\Nhave high spiritual energy...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.06,0:03:35.63,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,he attacks them and\Nincreases his own power.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.50,0:03:38.72,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,For over fifty years,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.72,0:03:41.75,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,this Hollow has defied Soul\NReapers like us.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.29,0:03:46.90,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,And his favorite is...women.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.34,0:03:50.38,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Which means...my mom was...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.00,0:03:58.46,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.80,0:04:02.18,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,You survived even after seeing me.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.18,0:04:04.29,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,What a lucky kid.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.96,0:04:07.35,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Perhaps at first I intended to\Ndevour you
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.35,0:04:09.63,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,for your\Nhigh spiritual energy.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.29,0:04:15.29,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,However...women always\Nseem more delicious.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.80,0:04:18.38,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Why that--!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.29,0:04:22.21,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Haven't seen a Hollow so disgusting\Nin a long time.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.92,0:04:31.72,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Karin!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.92,0:04:38.22,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Don't be so careless, you idiot!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.84,0:04:48.59,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Ichigo!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.34,0:04:54.75,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,You're one bastard\NI'll never forgive!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.29,0:05:01.29,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Disintegrate, you black dog\Nof Rondanini!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.29,0:05:02.99,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Look upon yourself and burn!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.99,0:05:05.13,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Tear out your own throat!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.75,0:05:07.75,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Binding Spell 9: Strike!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.17,0:05:16.34,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Do not interfere!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.29,0:05:30.64,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Now then, I'm going to\Ndevour this girl.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.64,0:05:31.84,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,What will you do?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.42,0:05:33.29,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Karin!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.46,0:05:38.78,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Stop!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.67,0:05:43.00,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Then will you let me eat you instead?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.29,0:06:02.24,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Karin!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.80,0:06:26.50,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Hey! You…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.30,0:06:31.94,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Why would you go that far...?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.46,0:06:37.71,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Soul Reapers keep fighting Hollows\Nno matter what happens.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.30,0:06:43.71,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Soul Reapers will never\Nforgive Hollows.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.46,0:06:48.17,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,When a Hollow attacks indiscriminately,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.75,0:06:53.29,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,and you lose something precious to you,\Nonly an empty feeling remains.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.29,0:06:56.13,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,I can't let that happen!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.55,0:07:03.13,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,You've gotta protect, Spiky...\Nyou understand?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.34,0:07:04.20,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Hey!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.29,0:07:06.90,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,No way...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.29,0:07:09.46,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,He can't have died if\Nhe's a Soul Reaper!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.46,0:07:13.42,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Even Soul Reapers are not immortal.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.29,0:07:16.05,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Even if the form is different,\Ndeath is...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.05,0:07:23.46,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,This guy’s asleep.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.42,0:07:27.05,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, get up! It’s distracting!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.71,0:07:28.38,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Sis!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.09,0:07:32.29,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Whoa... this looks pretty bad.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.09,0:07:35.43,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Kon! Take the sisters and run!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.46,0:07:39.34,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,What about you?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.34,0:07:40.96,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,– Hurry!\N– Right!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.80,0:07:48.05,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Ichigo, back me up.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.85,0:07:49.45,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Ichigo!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.38,0:07:53.29,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Rukia, get back.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.67,0:07:54.38,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.09,0:07:57.75,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Just stay back this time.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.88,0:08:00.39,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,I'll do it myself.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.63,0:08:03.00,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Don't be ridiculous! He is strong.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.29,0:08:04.06,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,I told you,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.06,0:08:06.43,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,he's been defying Soul Reapers\Nfor over fifty years--!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.43,0:08:07.37,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Shut up!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.42,0:08:10.34,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Please…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.92,0:08:13.29,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Don't interfere.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.29,0:08:15.21,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,This is...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.80,0:08:18.28,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,my fight!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.71,0:08:38.30,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Karin! A-Are you all right?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.09,0:08:46.88,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Cripes! Acting all serious\Nwith my eyebrows furrowed is tiring!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.29,0:08:50.46,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,How does Ichigo keep such\Nan expression for so long?!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.80,0:09:06.79,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,You're slow, kid!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.46,0:09:21.14,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,It was gutsy of you to\Ntell your friends
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.14,0:09:24.38,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,not to interfere when that's\Nthe limit of your strength.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.92,0:09:26.29,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Huh, kid?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.92,0:09:27.88,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Shut up…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.17,0:09:40.67,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,I don't really know\Nhow much Yuzu grieved after Mom died.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.21,0:09:45.09,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Or how lonely Karin felt.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.16,0:09:48.55,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,You gotta protect, Spiky.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.29,0:09:53.88,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,I decided to protect.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.24,0:10:01.65,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,I'm going to...\Ndestroy you!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.92,0:10:09.38,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Didn't your friend tell\Nyou not to be careless, kid?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.63,0:10:16.60,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Now how many times have\Nyou jumped right into the lion's den
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.60,0:10:19.00,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,without any strategy?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.50,0:10:25.20,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,That's why they call you careless, kid!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.13,0:10:57.84,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,You're too rash. Much too rash.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.10,0:11:01.06,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,You push away your comrade\Nin the heat of the moment,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.06,0:11:04.32,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,and jump right into your enemy's lair.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.32,0:11:08.29,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,You’ll just die while I toy you.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.35,0:11:11.38,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,– Ichigo!\N– Stay back!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.09,0:11:14.29,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Stay back, Rukia!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.84,0:11:16.09,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,I'm going to destroy him!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.29,0:11:19.34,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Even if my arms are ripped off...\Neven if my legs fly off.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.34,0:11:20.99,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,I'll beat him!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.99,0:11:24.13,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,And that's why I say you'll die.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.38,0:11:27.51,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Because you are young,\Nyou fly off the handle easily.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.51,0:11:30.18,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,And that passion distracts your heart.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.18,0:11:33.97,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,And a distracted heart dulls your sword.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.29,0:11:36.26,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,It's over, kid!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.26,0:11:40.38,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,You're much too young to be\Nfighting me!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.96,0:11:48.46,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Ichigo! That's…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.46,0:11:50.59,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Why you--!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.71,0:11:57.26,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Even the most cold-blooded\NSoul Reaper has one person
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.26,0:12:00.21,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,whom he can never kill.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.84,0:12:02.55,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,That is a certainty.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.43,0:12:05.64,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,By learning who that person is,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.64,0:12:09.05,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,I have been able to\Ndefy every Soul Reaper ‘til now.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.29,0:12:14.67,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,And for you, this person is the one.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.59,0:12:17.50,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Right…Ichigo?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.38,0:12:21.29,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Ichigo!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.96,0:12:24.09,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,And what of his honor?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.63,0:12:27.28,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,If you lend him your strength now,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.28,0:12:29.80,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,his life will\Nprobably be saved.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.30,0:12:35.00,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,But in doing so,\Nyou will forever destroy his honor.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.13,0:12:38.25,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Now listen and remember this.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.74,0:12:40.29,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,There are two kinds of battles.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.05,0:12:44.29,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,We must always distinguish\Nbetween the two.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.50,0:12:50.88,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,The battle to protect life...\Nand the battle to protect honor.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.21,0:12:57.42,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,That's right.\NThis is a battle to protect his honor.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.29,0:13:01.80,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,It is a battle in which\NI cannot lend him my strength.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.00,0:13:08.13,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Don't help him... don't help him...\Ndon't help him!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.29,0:13:13.29,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Don't die, Ichigo!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.84,0:13:21.75,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Oh dear, I fell asleep.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.34,0:13:24.29,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Damn!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.63,0:13:31.92,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Can you draw your sword\Nagainst this woman?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.42,0:13:34.29,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Why you--!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.96,0:13:37.29,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Do you realize what you're doing?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.29,0:13:39.42,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Don't you dare...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.29,0:13:44.29,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,bring my mom’s image out to\Na place like this!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.87,0:13:47.21,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,You must not, Ichigo.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.67,0:13:48.96,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Put down your sword.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.88,0:13:51.84,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Don't hurt your mother.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.05,0:13:55.88,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Please.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.71,0:14:16.92,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Didn't I tell you?\NAnger will dull your sword.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.71,0:14:20.38,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,It will be over with the next blow, kid.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.80,0:14:22.92,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,But I'll say this much for you.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.84,0:14:26.26,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Among those I have encountered,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.26,0:14:28.71,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,you were the youngest,\Nand the most rash...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.38,0:14:32.30,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,and the weakest Soul Reaper!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.29,0:14:34.02,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Ichigo!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.84,0:14:43.33,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,W-Wha--?!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.00,0:14:46.84,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,That’s…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.17,0:14:51.13,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Mom…?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.80,0:15:05.17,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,His mother's thoughts are\Nmanifesting themselves.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.42,0:15:08.13,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Does that mean the lure had\Nrecorded his mother's thoughts
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.29,0:15:10.36,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,at the moment of her death?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.42,0:15:13.29,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Thoughts at the moment of her death?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.38,0:15:17.30,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,I caught a glimpse of it earlier...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.38,0:15:20.59,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,No telling how this battle\Nis going to end yet.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.42,0:15:23.43,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Ichigo…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.63,0:15:29.71,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,I'm so proud of you!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.75,0:15:34.61,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Dad, Karin, Yuzu,\Nand you, Ichigo.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.84,0:15:40.59,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,I'm so proud that\NI was able to meet you.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.38,0:15:47.29,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Live, Ichigo.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.59,0:15:54.42,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,With strength, with kindness,\Nand with a smile…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.80,0:16:01.29,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you…Ichigo.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.29,0:16:15.96,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Ichigo…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.30,0:16:19.17,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Mom…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.29,0:16:23.29,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Is that what you were thinking\Nat that time...?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.88,0:16:28.09,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Anger dulls the sword...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.29,0:16:31.09,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,That may be true.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.67,0:16:34.67,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,However...you're wrong about one thing...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.29,0:16:37.42,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,In order to beat a thing like you,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.92,0:16:41.11,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,a dull sword is\Nmore than enough!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.63,0:16:47.39,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,If I were the rain…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.30,0:16:57.56,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,would I have been able to\Nconnect someone's heart
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.56,0:17:02.29,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,like the rain which connects\Nthe never-intersecting sky and earth?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.75,0:17:07.63,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Ichigo,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.34,0:17:13.25,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,I think I've come to understand\Nyou a bit more.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.06,0:17:27.71,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Dammit! Dammit!\NI won't forgive you!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.50,0:17:30.29,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,You're just a Soul Reaper!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.88,0:17:33.93,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Wait!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.17,0:17:37.92,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Ichigo!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.00,0:17:41.89,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Stop! That's enough.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.89,0:17:44.55,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Neither of you can fight any more.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.55,0:17:46.14,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,The battle is over!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.59,0:17:50.35,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Not yet! He's still not dead!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.71,0:17:51.39,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,I still--
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.39,0:17:52.29,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Ichigo!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.29,0:18:07.13,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,You lived, Ichigo… Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.42,0:18:10.10,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,He's something else.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.50,0:18:12.59,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,The power of the Soul Reaper's\Nspiritual energy
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.75,0:18:14.75,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,is the power of\Nhis life energy.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.00,0:18:18.29,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,This kid could become a monster.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.34,0:18:22.88,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Time to go home.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.29,0:18:28.05,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,I'm not so heartless as\Nto break up a serious couple.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.29,0:18:30.93,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,I guess, Rukia, you've come of age.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.93,0:18:31.84,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Don't even go there!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.92,0:18:35.21,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Well, whatever...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.21,0:18:37.29,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,When they find out, they find out.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.05,0:18:39.63,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Bye-bye!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.63,0:19:05.19,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry. I couldn't get revenge.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.17,0:19:07.13,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Mom...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.13,0:19:11.85,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Well, if you show yourself\Nlooking fit and healthy like that,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.85,0:19:13.88,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Mom will be relieved on the other side.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.29,0:19:17.67,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Don't eavesdrop on your own son.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.71,0:19:21.11,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,I thought you quit.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:25.88,0:19:28.92,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,When we first started dating\Nshe complimented me.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.46,0:19:31.88,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,She said that I looked cool\Nholding a cigarette.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.55,0:19:34.97,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Thinking back,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.97,0:19:39.32,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,that was the first and last time\Nyour mom ever complimented me.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.00,0:19:41.31,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,That's why I smoke just once,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.31,0:19:44.63,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,on this day every\Nyear in front of her.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.00,0:19:47.38,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,How can you keep smiling?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.75,0:19:50.71,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Why doesn't anyone blame me?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.34,0:19:53.29,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,It's hard to take!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.71,0:19:56.29,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,It'd be much easier if\Nyou all blamed me for this!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.59,0:19:57.29,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Why?!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.84,0:19:59.68,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Why should we blame you?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.68,0:20:00.29,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.42,0:20:04.76,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,If I blamed you for\Ncausing Masaki's death,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.76,0:20:07.05,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Masaki would scold me.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.84,0:20:10.88,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,It's no one's fault that\NMasaki died.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.19,0:20:14.93,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,She was...\Njust the woman I loved,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.93,0:20:18.29,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,who would give her life to\Nprotect her own child.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.13,0:20:22.47,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,And remember this:
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.55,0:20:28.29,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,You are the man whom the woman I loved\Nprotected with her life.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.05,0:20:30.05,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Dad...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.67,0:20:34.88,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Oww…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:35.29,0:20:37.09,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Live well, Ichigo…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:39.05,0:20:41.29,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Live well, grow old well,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:41.29,0:20:44.96,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,go bald well, and then die after me.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:47.05,0:20:49.34,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,And if you can, die laughing.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:49.34,0:20:52.13,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Otherwise, I won't be able to face Masaki.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:52.75,0:20:54.17,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Shake off your depression.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:54.34,0:20:56.49,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,You're way too young\Nto be burdened
Dialogue: 0,0:20:56.49,0:20:58.29,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,by something cool like sadness.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:59.13,0:21:00.29,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,I'll be waiting below.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:05.17,0:21:07.09,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Are you listening, Rukia?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:08.05,0:21:11.59,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Let me be a Soul Reaper\Nfor a while longer.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:12.25,0:21:13.80,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,I want to become strong.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:14.42,0:21:18.46,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,I want to become strong and\Nprotect people from Hollows!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:18.80,0:21:20.29,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Those who are attacked by them.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:20.96,0:21:22.29,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,And I'm going to beat him!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:23.29,0:21:27.30,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Otherwise...\NI won't be able to face my mom!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:31.88,0:21:32.87,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Ichigo…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:59.23,0:22:03.78,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Though the voyage must continue on
Dialogue: 0,0:22:04.49,0:22:08.31,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,May seas always be calm
Dialogue: 0,0:22:08.65,0:22:13.71,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,When the cycle of the moon\Nhas renewed may it shine
Dialogue: 0,0:22:13.71,0:22:18.58,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,It's light to guide your boat
Dialogue: 0,0:22:18.97,0:22:23.40,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,I offer this voyage a prayer
Dialogue: 0,0:22:23.40,0:22:28.35,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,With each new day that still awaits
Dialogue: 0,0:22:28.35,0:22:32.48,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,On vividly shining seas
Dialogue: 0,0:22:32.74,0:22:39.49,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,To the end of the journey
Dialogue: 0,0:22:39.94,0:22:42.87,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Wow! What a scary Hollow that was!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:42.87,0:22:45.22,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,I was pitiful in this episode,
Dialogue: 0,0:22:45.22,0:22:48.60,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,but next time,\Ncome hell or high water,
Dialogue: 0,0:22:48.60,0:22:52.30,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,I'll show my stuff, for Rukia's sake!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:52.21,0:22:54.22,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,– There're no scenes for you next time.\N– Huh?!